  <h1>Welcome to MaybDo</h1>
  <p style="color: green">Organize your tasks in a fun and engaging way with our daily challenges. It all starts with the powerful question:</p>
  <p>What might you do today?</p>

  <div class="cta-buttons">
    <%= link_to 'Sign Up', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
